      "sourceText": [
        [
          "5 days ago Kristine Dica Verified Customer One of the best coffee, and our favorite to buy for home brewing.",
          "I found about the Assembly coffee while drinking it a Kaffeine, Miel and Brityard.",
          "I loved their coffee and then I found out they all use the same coffee brand: Assembly coffee beans.",
          "Since then I am a loyal customer.",
          "😁 1 week ago Adomas Paltanavicius Verified Customer I did the SCA Sensory Skills training at Assembly with Raquel.",
          "Raquel was happy to answer all the questions I've had and provide additional references for more in-depth reading where relevant.",
          "2 weeks ago Axel Dopfer Verified Customer Assmebly coffee kickstarted my now fully fledged coffee obsession.",
          "Excellent coffee made by excellent people.",
          "3 weeks ago Raphael Eder Verified Customer NANANANAdddd 3 weeks ago Bharat Mehta Verified Customer Great coffees.",
          "Wonderful service 4 weeks ago Anna Bortiana Verified Customer good quality coffee, good client service!",
          "1 month ago Anonymous Verified Customer Excellent coffee fast shipping.",
          "Best decaffeinated coffee I ever tasted.",
          "1 month ago Tiago Salviano Calmon Verified Customer The session was quite enjoyable.",
          "1 month ago Ian toogood Verified Customer Very impressed with the operation.",
          "The coffees are interesting and diverse and the service in excellent.",
          "1 month ago Anonymous Verified Customer Great overall experience.",
          "Only suggestion is to increase their decaf offering if possible.",
          "1 month ago Dawn Carman Verified Customer Have tried a few different coffee roasters but Assembly is the best.",
          "2 months ago Ernest Onyeforo Verified Customer Superb coffee drip bags.",
          "The flavour profile was one of the best I’ve had across any roasters.",
          "Definitely makes me want to purchase more.",
          "2 months ago John Buller Verified Customer I use the espresso blend and it's been a staple for my coffee machine for the last few years.",
          "2 months ago Winnie Wong Verified Customer Responsive customer service.",
          "The Ethiopia Rumudamo has a sweet fragrance and long after taste.",
          "It brightens my weekend.",
          "2 months ago Liam Moyna Verified Customer Bought subminimal scales to get away from having a separate vessel hold my beans in.",
          "Works very well and is small enough to pack away in a bag and very light.",
          "My Bookoo ultra is quite heavy in comparison.",
          "Well packed and good tracking.",
          "Through essays, analysis, and original research, Issue 01 explores the forces, systems and narratives defining the present and shaping the future."
        ]
